Package net.mtrop.doom.text

Class EternityMapInfo

java.lang.Object
net.mtrop.doom.text.EternityMapInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Map.Entry<String,MapInfoData[]>>, TextObject
public class EternityMapInfo extends Object implements TextObject, Iterable<Map.Entry<String,MapInfoData[]>>
An abstraction of the Eternity Map Info entry (EMAPINFO). Entry headers are stored case-insensitively, for convenience.
Since:
2.19.0
Author:
Matthew Tropiano
